Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 早上好\N{\fs38}Morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 警监\N{\fs38}Morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪\N{\fs38}Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱俩衣服都洒上吃的了\N{\fs38}We're food stain buds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么吃的 粥吗\N{\fs38}Who are you wearing? Porridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是\N{\fs38}Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燕麦\N{\fs38}oatmeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs38}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都不擦掉的\N{\fs38}He didn't even wipe it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经放弃人生了吧\N{\fs38}He's totally given up on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是孤单\N{\fs38}It's loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从Kevin离开他去了巴黎休假\N{\fs38}Ever since Kevin left for his sabbatical in Paris,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟变了个人似的\N{\fs38}he hasn't been the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让他多出去参加些活动\N{\fs38}I tried to get him out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请他去参加酒吧问答 但他拒绝了我\N{\fs38}I invited him to bar trivia, but he turned me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说我们"牛顿谜语队"需要他做外援\N{\fs38}not that Trivia Newton John needed the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是全国排名靠前的队伍 没啥大不了的\N{\fs38}We're nationally ranked. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没什么大不了的\N{\fs38}You're right, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都只是些好心的小傻瓜们\N{\fs38}Well, aren't you all just a bunch of big-hearted dum-dums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想让他不那么寂寞\N{\fs38}You want to make him feel less lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该这么做\N{\fs38}This is how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一袋卷宗  - 对 他是工作狂\N{\fs38}- A case file? - Yeah, dude loves work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你的案子都结了\N{\fs38}I thought all your cases were closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨晚一直在炫耀这事\N{\fs38}You were bragging about it so much last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居吵架我都没听到结局\N{\fs38}I couldn't hear the end of the neighbors' fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结局就是俩人做爱了 他们总是那样\N{\fs38}It ended in sex. It always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我完全没性趣\N{\fs38}It didn't make me horny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一年当警探的一个旧案子\N{\fs38}It's a cold case from my first year as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪犯又有新活动了\N{\fs38}Is it active again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 但Holt不需要知道这点\N{\fs38}No, but Holt doesn't have to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你打算撒谎\N{\fs38}So you're gonna lie to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要用一种方法 让他忘却悲伤\N{\fs38}No, I'm going to make him forget about his sadness through the power of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 分散注意力\N{\fs38}distraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我消失啦\N{\fs38}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 早上好\N{\fs38}Ah, hola, mi capitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会问 为什么我要说意大利语\N{\fs38}Why am I speaking Italian, you might ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是西班牙语\N{\fs38}That was Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 语言种类千千万嘛\N{\fs38}Yeah, there are too many languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一个旧案子有新进展了\N{\fs38}An old case of mine is starting to heat up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要您老来帮助我 先生\N{\fs38}and I'd like your old help to help me solve it, senor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还是西班牙语  - 好吧\N{\fs38}- Still Spanish. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Joey Garibaldi曾经是个黑帮头目\N{\fs38}Joey Garibaldi was a mafia lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多八年前 我已经快抓到他了\N{\fs38}About eight years ago, I was closing in on him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却销声匿迹了\N{\fs38}when he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可现在我又听到风声\N{\fs38}But now I'm hearing chatter on the street
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他又冒头了\N{\fs38}that he's back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我吗\N{\fs38}Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听上去挺有趣 算我一个\N{\fs38}Hmm, sounds interesting. Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 谢谢\N{\fs38}Yes! Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见咯\N{\fs38}Uh, good-a bye-a.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是意大利语\N{\fs38}Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,标准化测试吗\N{\fs38}Ooh, standardized tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个小诀窍\N{\fs38}I have a great trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿涂改液涂满所有格子\N{\fs38}Fill in all the bubbles with Wite-Out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再对读卡器动点手脚 大家都能过\N{\fs38}jams the machine, everyone passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的警督考试的练习题\N{\fs38}These are practice for the lieutenant's exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太难了\N{\fs38}They're kicking my butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直考不到70分\N{\fs38}I can't get better than 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C减 这是最完美的分数了\N{\fs38}C-minus, the perfect grade--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明你有点头脑 但还是性感的\N{\fs38}you pass, but you're still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Holt警监给了我他的卷子来帮我\N{\fs38}Captain Holt gave me his test to help me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧阅卷人给他写的评语\N{\fs38}Look at what the grader wrote on his essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"感谢你写了这篇文章\N{\fs38}"Thank you for writing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它帮助我成为更好的人"\N{\fs38}Reading it made me a better man."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会成为和Holt一样优秀的领导的\N{\fs38}I'll never be as good a leader as Holt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要老想着考试了\N{\fs38}You need to stop focusing on tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活中不只有分数和书本\N{\fs38}There's more to life than scores and book learning, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我 我从没上过专业舞蹈课\N{\fs38}Look at me, I've had no official dance training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在\N{\fs38}Yet here I stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是舞动的奇迹\N{\fs38}a miracle of movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看见Boyle了吗\N{\fs38}Hey, you guys seen Boyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在他桌子底下呢 缩成球了\N{\fs38}Yep, he's in a little ball under his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fs38}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.48,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,NBC悬疑剧\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨晚又看<格林>了\N{\fs38}Did you watch "Grimm" Again last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知道看了会做噩梦的\N{\fs38}You know it gives you nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好伤心\N{\fs38}I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jason今早去世了\N{\fs38}Jason died this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 太惨了\N{\fs38}I'm sorry. That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的朋友吗\N{\fs38}Is he a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的狗狗\N{\fs38}He was my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那就不是什么大事\N{\fs38}Oh, okay, so no big deal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是大事\N{\fs38}No, it is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不用担心\N{\fs38}But don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想办法挺过去的\N{\fs38}I'll find a way to power through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jason就是以这个视角看世界的\N{\fs38}This is how Jason saw the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 Jason就是那条什么都操的狗\N{\fs38}Wait, was this your dog that humped everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他就是这么死的\N{\fs38}Yeah, that's how he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本想上我的一双雪地靴\N{\fs38}He was going to town on one of my snow boots,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他的小心脏没承受住\N{\fs38}and his little heart just gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他都还没射呢  - 真恶心\N{\fs38}- He didn't even finish. - Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们要去四街的那家运动用品商店去跟线索\N{\fs38}Anyway, we have to work a stream of B&E's on 4th Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该向前看了\N{\fs38}It's time for you to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jackson会是这么希望的\N{\fs38}It's what Jackson would've wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他叫Jason  - 无所谓 小伙计\N{\fs38}- Jason! - Whatever, little buddy.
