Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 谢谢你来见我\N{\fs38}Captain, thank you for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你周六加班了 真是不好意思\N{\fs38}Sorry to make you work on a Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说 反正我很闲\N{\fs38}No, nonsense, I was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kevin还在巴黎\N{\fs38}Kevin is still in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs38}Is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不记得了呢\N{\fs38}Wow, I totally forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 这就是Garibaldi销声匿迹后\N{\fs38}Any-hoops, this is all the stuff that we got
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在他公寓找到的全部东西了\N{\fs38}from Garibaldi's apartment after he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你有什么发现\N{\fs38}Tell me what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人在每张照片里都出现过\N{\fs38}This man is in every photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nick DiTullio{\fs38}\NNick DiTullio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我八年前就带他去问过话\N{\fs38}I actually brought him in eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他什么都不肯说\N{\fs38}but he refused to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的 俗话说的好\N{\fs38}Of course, you know the saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时间会让每个男人开口的\N{\fs38}"Time shall open up the mouth of every man
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是关于他邻居的真相"\N{\fs38}to the truth of his neighbor."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有这么个俗语的 就别计较这个了\N{\fs38}All right, it's a real saying. Let's not dwell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是 他肯定会告诉我们Garibaldi的下落\N{\fs38}The point is, he's definitely gonna tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道Garibaldi在哪\N{\fs38}I don't know where Garibaldi is, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走得并不近\N{\fs38}It's not like we were close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是他的健身教练而已\N{\fs38}I was just his trainer at the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们为什么经常一起去吃饭\N{\fs38}Then why were you always going out to dinner with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 吃意大利面也算健身吗  - 问得好\N{\fs38}- Was he doing reps of linguine? - Noice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝Garibaldi是不可能的 明白吗\N{\fs38}Look, you don't say no to Garibaldi, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我只让他练胸肌和腹肌\N{\fs38}That's why I always let him work his chest and his abs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从不练腿部\N{\fs38}and never his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 关键在于平衡\N{\fs38}Yeah, the key is balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我从来不练肌肉\N{\fs38}That's why I never work any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们不是来逮捕我的话 我得先走了\N{\fs38}Unless you guys are gonna arrest me, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健身房那边出了些紧急情况\N{\fs38}There's an emergency at the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个警察来问话 健身房正好出现紧急情况\N{\fs38}Emergency at the gym just when two cops show up at his door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很可疑 我们应该跟踪他\N{\fs38}That seems suspicious. We should follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这案子还真出现了线索\N{\fs38}Yeah, this case might actually lead somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么这么惊讶\N{\fs38}Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这份工作每天都充满惊奇\N{\fs38}Because every day on this job is a wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能更同意了\N{\fs38}Damn right it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医学检测员 我们中奖了\N{\fs38}Medical examiner, jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那健身房里肯定全是尸体\N{\fs38}The gym is full of bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是卫生部  - 哦 天哪\N{\fs38}- No, Department of Health. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很流行腮腺炎\N{\fs38}There's been an outbreak of the mumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腮腺炎 这词太搞笑了\N{\fs38}Mumps, that's a funny word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其实是一个很容易传染的重病\N{\fs38}It's actually a very serious and highly contagious infectious disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们不会被传染的\N{\fs38}Yeah, but we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也就和那人接触了几秒钟\N{\fs38}We were only in contact with that guy for a couple of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 他也没舔我们眼球\N{\fs38}Plus, he didn't even lick any of our eyeballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们恐怕都得了腮腺炎\N{\fs38}I'm afraid you both have the mumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腮腺炎 听起来还是很搞笑\N{\fs38}Mumps, still a funny word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会死吧\N{\fs38}Are we gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你们都得了腮腺炎\N{\fs38}So you both have the mumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 这病传染性很强\N{\fs38}Sorry to say, it's very contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警探 你可能不想呆在这里\N{\fs38}You may not want to be here, detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 没关系的\N{\fs38}Oh, it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我定期打疫苗\N{\fs38}I keep up to date on all my vaccinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对很多你们听都没听过的病免疫呢\N{\fs38}I'm immune to stuff you've never even heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了爱吹牛的病\N{\fs38}But not immune to braggadocio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 接下来的几个小时内\N{\fs38}Anyhow, over the next several hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很可能会有发烧 疼痛 疲劳的症状\N{\fs38}you will more than likely develop fever, aching, fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不算什么\N{\fs38}Doesn't sound too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 酸性食物会带来严重的下颚疼痛\N{\fs38}Also, tart foods will cause intense jaw pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们最好别吃酸的糖果\N{\fs38}so you may want to avoid sour candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则脖子上可能会长甲状腺肿块 很疼\N{\fs38}You may get painful goiter-like swelling in your neck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 还可能发生睾丸部位的不适\N{\fs38}and often extreme testicular discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 懂了\N{\fs38}- Okay, okay. - Cool, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂 懂 懂\N{\fs38}Cool, cool, cool, cool, cool, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问\N{\fs38}No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这病毒有极高的传染性\N{\fs38}Due the highly contagious nature of the virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来九天 你们两位将会在家进行隔离\N{\fs38}you will both be quarantined to your houses for the next nine days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 孤独的九天\N{\fs38}Oh, nine days in isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 我很乐意去陪你\N{\fs38}Sir, I'd be happy to keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:18.08,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,<Nicholas Nickleby>是英国作家狄更斯所写的小说，被多次改编成影视剧作。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以看PBS电视台播的Nicholas Nickleby传记十部曲\N{\fs38}We can watch the ten-part Nicholas Nickleby special on PBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说电影节奏又慢 时间又长\N{\fs38}Hear there's a lot of long, quiet stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实喜欢慢节奏时间长的电影\N{\fs38}I do love long, quiet stretches,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不想成为累赘\N{\fs38}but I don't want to be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我越来越习惯独处了\N{\fs38}Plus, I'm getting used to being on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们可以一起被隔离\N{\fs38}Or we could be quarantined together, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便把案子办了\N{\fs38}work the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 这听上去有点意思\N{\fs38}Yes, that actually sounds kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是"有点"意思吗\N{\fs38}Kind of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是爽翻天的一周\N{\fs38}It's gonna be the best week ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你们没听到我之前提到的\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, did you not hear me say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"睾丸部位的极度不适"吗\N{\fs38}extreme testicular discomfort?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听到了 "坏消息"医生\N{\fs38}Yes, we heard you, Dr. Bad News Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和Holt警监刚通了话\N{\fs38}Okay, so I talked to Captain Holt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和Jake都得了腮腺炎\N{\fs38}He and Jake have the mumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在Holt康复之前我全权负责\N{\fs38}I'm in charge until Holt gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好事啊 你想知道自己是否能成为一个优秀的警监\N{\fs38}Hello, you wanted to see if you can make a great captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你发光发亮的机会\N{\fs38}Now's your chance to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个漂亮的小替角\N{\fs38}You're the pretty little understudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那个老去的主角\N{\fs38}And the aging lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚从楼梯上摔了下去\N{\fs38}Well, she just fell down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你要做的是挥着你的翅膀\N{\fs38}Now all's you got to do is beat those wings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞翔\N{\fs38}and fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来两周\N{\fs38}So for the next two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Holt警监要休病假\N{\fs38}Captain Holt will be on medical leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监一职由我代理\N{\fs38}which means I am the acting captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是您忠诚的臣民\N{\fs38}And we are your royal subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续\N{\fs38}Do continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望大家不仅做好本职工作\N{\fs38}I want this precinct to get our normal work done,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要清理证据室\N{\fs38}but also, we're gonna clean out the evidence room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完善社区服务\N{\fs38}step up community service,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时完成另外22项任务\N{\fs38}and complete these 22 additional tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每完成一项打个勾\N{\fs38}Every time we check one off the list,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会听到铃声\N{\fs38}you're gonna hear this bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它象征着胜利\N{\fs38}It's the sound of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该再加条"修理铃铛"\N{\fs38}Hmm, you should add "Fix bell" to that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.76,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(2.331,584.833,239.911,582.157,5,214)}隔离期 第2天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 早上好 警监  - Peralta\N{\fs38}- Morning, Captain. - Peralta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给你介绍个人\N{\fs38}I'd like to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫Simon 我恨死他了\N{\fs38}His name is Simon, and I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Simon\N{\fs38}Hello, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Balthazar\N{\fs38}This is Balthazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个往我喉咙里喷火的恶魔\N{\fs38}He's an evil demon who spits fire in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲状腺肿了吧\N{\fs38}Goiters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你说啦\N{\fs38}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这些餐厅照片都看了一遍\N{\fs38}I've been looking over these photographs of the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定了其他几个已知的犯罪团伙\N{\fs38}and I've identified several other known mob types.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你发现了什么\N{\fs38}What is it? Did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 我就是突然好冷打了个颤\N{\fs38}No, I just got very cold very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在全身火烧火燎的\N{\fs38}And now my entire body is somehow on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腮腺炎讨厌死了\N{\fs38}Oh, these mumps are jerks. Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在其他几张照片里注意到有辆货车停在餐厅前面\N{\fs38}I also noticed this van is parked out front in several other photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么没注意到\N{\fs38}I never noticed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家餐厅肯定被监视了\N{\fs38}The restaurant must have been under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估计是政府的人\N{\fs38}I bet it was the feds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs38}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去联系局里认识的人\N{\fs38}I'll reach out to my contact at the bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看能不能拿到点录像\N{\fs38}see if I can get us some footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fs38}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对 虽然知道不可以\N{\fs38}Also, I know you're not supposed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我好想戳戳自己的腮腺炎\N{\fs38}but I kind of want to poke my mump.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 别想了  - 我要戳了\N{\fs38}- Bad idea. - I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要戳了\N{\fs38}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了\N{\fs38}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到会这么疼\N{\fs38}How did I not see that coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点儿晕\N{\fs38}I feel dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你终于爬起来了\N{\fs38}Hey. You're off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我爸以前常说的\N{\fs38}Well, it's like my dad used to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"是男人就别哭\N{\fs38}"Real men don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过三天"\N{\fs38}for more than three days."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定重振旗鼓回来工作\N{\fs38}So I decided to get my butt back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 你把目击证词都看过了吗\N{\fs38}Good. You go through all the witness statements yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 没有\N{\fs38}What? Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"工作"是指制作Jason的纪念视频\N{\fs38}By "Work," I meant on Jason's in memoriam video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你认真的吗  - 当然\N{\fs38}- Are you serious? - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你看我做好的\N{\fs38}Take a look at what I got so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:09:00.20,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael Bolton <How Am I Supposed to Live without You>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*告诉我没有你我要怎么活*\N{\fs38}*Tell me how am I supposed to live without you*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我已经爱了你这么久*\N{\fs38}*Now that I've been lovin' you so long*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.12,屏字2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(635.328,469.74)\frz356.2\frx356\fry350\c&HF569D0&}永远想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有好多事要做呢\N{\fs38}Hey, we've got a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中注意力 别再看搞笑的小狗视频了\N{\fs38}Focus up and stop watching funny dog videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我烧傻了\N{\fs38}This might just be the fever talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这家意大利餐厅八年前未剪辑的镜头\N{\fs38}but this unedited footage of an Italian restaurant\N可能是我烧傻了\N{\fs38}This might just be the fever talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这家意大利餐厅八年前未剪辑的镜头\N{\fs38}but this unedited footage of an Italian restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我看过的最棒的电影了\N{\fs38}from eight years ago might be the best movie I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 用叉子多怪啊\N{\fs38}Also, how weird are forks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉子是很诡异 我一直这么觉得\N{\fs38}Forks are very weird. I've always thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错 我们是不是感冒药吃多了\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah. Did we take too much cold medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fs38}Not by a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Balthazar可是个饥渴的小贱人\N{\fs38}Balthazar is a thirsty bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你这句喝一杯\N{\fs38}Ah, I'll drink to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 看啊\N{\fs38}Wait, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Garkabargo\N{\fs38}Garkabargo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 没 没法儿说话\N{\fs38}Sorry, can't--can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要次药\N{\fs38}Need more medi-jen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Garibaldi\N{\fs38}Garibaldi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在吃蛇啊\N{\fs38}He's eating snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是意面\N{\fs38}No, it's spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远都在吃意面\N{\fs38}It's always spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说 如果是意面 那也长得太像蛇了\N{\fs38}I'm just saying, if that's spaghetti, it looks like snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 99\N{\fs38}That's right, Nine-Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利的铃声欣然响起\N{\fs38}That's the sound of the victory bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完成了清单里的一个任务\N{\fs38}We just crossed our first task off the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天 Terry 太棒了\N{\fs38}Oh, my goodness. Terry, that is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪一项\N{\fs38}Which one was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 修理铃铛  - 好的吧\N{\fs38}- Fix bell. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点小失望 但总算完成一项了\N{\fs38}Little less than I had hoped for, but still a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你会一直听到这铃声的\N{\fs38}You gonna hear that sound nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 放开她 你这野兽  - 给我\N{\fs38}- Unhand her, you beast! - Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们他妈在干嘛\N{\fs38}What the hell is going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hitchcock想偷我的三明治\N{\fs38}Hitchcock's trying to steal my sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪 我俩都点了肉球三明治\N{\fs38}Well, we both ordered meatball subs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只送来了一个\N{\fs38}but they only delivered one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的\N{\fs38}It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们 听着 走去三明治店\N{\fs38}Guys, guys, look, just walk to the sub shop--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条街的事儿 再买个三明治\N{\fs38}it's a block away-- and get a second sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走去  - 疯了吗你\N{\fs38}- Walk? - Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧 切两半总行了吧\N{\fs38}Fine, cut the damn sandwich in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 机灵鬼 我们一人吃6英寸三明治\N{\fs38}And then what, genius? We each eat a 6-inch sub?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和两个半肉球\N{\fs38}Two and a half meatballs a piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你当我们小孩儿吗  - 你以为自己在俄罗斯吗\N{\fs38}- Are we children? - What is this, Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 都不许吃\N{\fs38}Okay, that's it. No one eats the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去工作\N{\fs38}Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.86,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(-1.335,582.156,242.476,580.818,40,249)}隔离期 第5天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下\N{\fs38}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他去了厨房\N{\fs38}Why'd he just go in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在厨房也有眼线吗\N{\fs38}Do we have eyes in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都有眼线\N{\fs38}There are eyes everywhere, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卧 槽 疼 死 了\N{\fs38}Ow, ow, achy, achy, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 他偷偷塞给大厨一张纸条\N{\fs38}Look, he slipped the chef a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜上面就是他的藏匿地点了\N{\fs38}I bet it's the address of his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厨知道他藏在哪儿\N{\fs38}The chef knows where the hideout is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厨叫Richie Lignardi\N{\fs38}His name is Richie Lignardi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到他 就能找到Garibaldi\N{\fs38}We talk to him, we find Garibaldi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就出发\N{\fs38}We have to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么发\N{\fs38}Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 你脸上是什么\N{\fs38}Ah! What's on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对 恶心的畸形肿块\N{\fs38}Oh, right, uh, yes, my disgusting deformity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我这样\N{\fs38}Here, let me just--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你好吗 大妹子\N{\fs38}Hey, what's up, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有好一点\N{\fs38}Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没差啦\N{\fs38}It's not worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们准备去找线人\N{\fs38}We're on our way right now to talk to a lead
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道Garibaldi藏在哪儿\N{\fs38}that knows where Garibaldi's hideout is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还在隔离期啊\N{\fs38}You're quarantined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能像两座腮腺炎喷泉一样\N{\fs38}You can't go outside spewing mumps
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腮腺炎喷得到处都是啊\N{\fs38}like a couple of mump fountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是肯定不行的\N{\fs38}Not like this, we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 你们不能走\N{\fs38}Stop, you can't leave at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止得了你就试试呗\N{\fs38}Good luck trying to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抓不到我们哒\N{\fs38}You'll never catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.48,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Usain Bolt 奥运会男子100米和200米记录保持者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amy快得像Usain Bolt\N{\fs38}Amy is Usain Bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们要找的纸条吗\N{\fs38}Is this the piece of paper you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到地址啦\N{\fs38}You found the address?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 这是烤通心粉的菜谱\N{\fs38}No, it's a recipe for baked ziti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直贴在你墙上的啊\N{\fs38}It was taped to your wall the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们太虚弱了 病得不轻\N{\fs38}You're delirious, and you're sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是破不了案的\N{\fs38}and you definitely didn't solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我回去\N{\fs38}You need to go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到 腿动不了了\N{\fs38}Well, I can't. My legs stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的蛋蛋\N{\fs38}Ah, my testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腮腺炎扩散到蛋蛋了\N{\fs38}The mumps have reached my testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把毫无用处\N{\fs38}All right, just finish taking off your totally ineffective
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还带着传染源的外套脱了 休息一下\N{\fs38}biohazard suits and have a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡扯 Santiago\N{\fs38}Nonsense, Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得勒紧裤腰 努力工作\N{\fs38}We just have to buckle down and work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是受了点小挫折\N{\fs38}We simply hit a bump in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更像受了点腮腺炎\N{\fs38}More like a mump in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼得厉害吧\N{\fs38}Such a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jake 能跟你私聊一下吗\N{\fs38}Jake, can I talk to you in private for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我拿条围巾 把肿块挡挡\N{\fs38}Sure thing, let me just snag this, cover up the ol' swell sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 情况是这样的\N{\fs38}Okay, so here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发高烧了 控制不了身体\N{\fs38}I have a high fever, and I can't control my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对我做什么都行\N{\fs38}but you can do whatever you want to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 别碰我的嘴 脖子 和蛋蛋\N{\fs38}Oh, but don't touch my mouth, neck, or testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全误会我的意思了\N{\fs38}You've badly misread the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\N{\fs38}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jake 放弃这个案子吧\N{\fs38}Jake, you need to drop this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢你\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的计划实施得很完美\N{\fs38}The plan is working perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Holt这一周都没闲着\N{\fs38}Holt hasn't been lonely all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 因为他忙得快挂了\N{\fs38}Yeah, because he's too busy almost dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你看他  - 怎么了\N{\fs38}- Look at him. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他像<美丽心灵>的主角一样\N{\fs38}He's just "Beautiful Mind"-ing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是天才啊\N{\fs38}Because he's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在不停地写"案子"这俩字\N{\fs38}He's writing the word "Case" Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 他开始写"安子"了\N{\fs38}Oh, now he's spelling it with a K.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是这么写的吗\N{\fs38}Is that not how you spell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 我烧得嘴 脖子和蛋蛋都要融化了\N{\fs38}Again, I have a mouth, neck, and testicle-melting fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Jake  - 怎么\N{\fs38}- Jake. - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止\N{\fs38}Enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃这个蠢逼无聊的旧案子\N{\fs38}You need to drop this stupid backburner cold case
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则要么你们死 要么我就杀了你\N{\fs38}before you both die or I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我天 我还以为自己跟上她的思维了呢\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, I thought I was following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我还是躺下吧\N{\fs38}Yep, I should probably lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 躺\N{\fs38}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案子\N{\fs38}Case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fs38}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Jason的项圈密封在袋子里\N{\fs38}Just sealing Jason's collar in an airtight bag
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能留住他的气味\N{\fs38}so it retains his scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道我还剩多少味道能闻了\N{\fs38}I don't know how many whiffs I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊\N{\fs38}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那条狗对你来说很重要\N{\fs38}Look, I know that dog meant a lot to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我给你带了这个\N{\fs38}so I got you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只狗\N{\fs38}It's a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫Arlo 但是你也可以叫他Jason二号\N{\fs38}His name's Arlo, but you can call him Jason Two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者其他名字\N{\fs38}or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真的\N{\fs38}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能就这么随便地用另一只狗来代替Jason\N{\fs38}I can't just replace Jason with some other dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 基本上所有狗都一样\N{\fs38}Why not? All dogs are basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了 Arlo 快去干那个玩具\N{\fs38}Watch this. Arlo, go hump that toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰它\N{\fs38}Get away from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Jason的\N{\fs38}That's Jason's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 伙计 我已经很耐心了\N{\fs38}Look, man, I've been patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有个案子要查\N{\fs38}We have a case we need to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候忘了这件事朝前看了\N{\fs38}It's time for you to get over it, move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝前看 朝前看\N{\fs38}Move on? Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jason是我家的一份子 Rosa\N{\fs38}Jason was part of my family, Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱他\N{\fs38}I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他发情是唯一能让我撑过离婚的动力\N{\fs38}His humping was the only thing that got me through my divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见他那么开心我就觉得\N{\fs38}Seeing him so happy made me believe
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有一天我也能那么开心\N{\fs38}that I could be happy one day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会明白这种感受的\N{\fs38}You wouldn't understand this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你有摩托车头盔来抵御真心\N{\fs38}because you have a motorcycle helmet for a heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我需要感受这份悲伤\N{\fs38}but I need to feel this sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我现在唯一要离开向前看的就是你\N{\fs38}So the only thing that I'm moving on from is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我好像 有了一只狗\N{\fs38}So I, like, have a dog now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那些文件看得怎么样了\N{\fs38}Hey, what's going on with those files?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没在研究那些\N{\fs38}Oh, we're not working on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们在罢工  - 绝食抗议\N{\fs38}- We're on strike. - Hunger strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 可你在吃薯片  - 薯片不算数\N{\fs38}- You're eating potato chips. - Chips don't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的医生说薯片一点营养价值都没有\N{\fs38}My doctor said they have zero nutritional value.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要肉丸三明治\N{\fs38}We want meatball subs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有权利拿走我们的食物\N{\fs38}You had no right to take ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死我吧\N{\fs38}Screw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会整理好这些文件 教危险品的课程\N{\fs38}I'll log those files and teach the hazmat class,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把所有人的活儿都干了 因为很明显\N{\fs38}and I'll do everyone's work, because apparently,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是唯一一个能让这个分局凝聚在一起的人\N{\fs38}I am the only one keeping this precinct together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我觉得你关门太用力了\N{\fs38}Um, I think you closed the door too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了雪糕\N{\fs38}Hey, I found popsicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该能帮我们降温\N{\fs38}These should help cool us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦 Jake\N{\fs38}"Thanks, Jake."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气 蛋蛋君\N{\fs38}You're welcome, nards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peralta Balthzar有个姐妹\N{\fs38}Peralta, Balthazar has a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做Penelope\N{\fs38}Meet Penelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 你两边都肿了\N{\fs38}Guh-hoo, yeah, mumps on mumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意细节 我们赶紧开始工作\N{\fs38}Let's not dwell on it. We should get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们也可以睡个五到七天\N{\fs38}Or we could fall asleep for five to seven days
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看看感觉如何\N{\fs38}and see how we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义得到伸张之前我不会休息的\N{\fs38}I will not rest till justice is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别浪费时间了\N{\fs38}There's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个案子非常紧急\N{\fs38}This case is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天\N{\fs38}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 听好了\N{\fs38}All right, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个案子其实没我们开始想的那么紧急\N{\fs38}The case may not be quite as urgent as once thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs38}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我从桌上挖出来\N{\fs38}I dug it up out of my desk so you'd have something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你在周末有些事做的 因为你看起来非常孤单\N{\fs38}to do on weekends because you seemed so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说Garibaldi卷土重来了\N{\fs38}You cited chatter from the streets that Garibaldi had resurfaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 没错 就是这样\N{\fs38}I did. I did. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那些可能只是胡说八道\N{\fs38}But said chatter may have been fudged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你骗了我\N{\fs38}So you lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出于同情 你同情我\N{\fs38}Out of pity. You pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话不是这么说的\N{\fs38}I wouldn't put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这么觉得的\N{\fs38}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受到了冒犯 我很生气\N{\fs38}I am offended. I am angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很累\N{\fs38}I am very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要睡一觉 但当我醒来\N{\fs38}So I'm gonna take a nap, but when I wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为此付出代价\N{\fs38}oh, you are in for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.70,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(717.427,433.513)}4小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么敢\N{\fs38}How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么敢\N{\fs38}How dare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么敢\N{\fs38}How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要帮忙\N{\fs38}I was just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的帮助感觉太像同情了\N{\fs38}Wow, your help feels an awful lot like pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以帮帮忙 别再帮我了\N{\fs38}so do me a favor and don't ever help me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 你好像不在意我帮你\N{\fs38}Wow, well, you didn't seem to mind me helping you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回你在99分局的工作\N{\fs38}when I got you your job back at the Nine-Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没要你帮忙\N{\fs38}I didn't ask you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我们没有豆子了 你这个偷豆子的猪\N{\fs38}You said we were out of peas, you pea hog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你才是偷豆子的猪  - 你才是偷豆子的猪\N{\fs38}- You're the pea hog! - You're the pea hog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 你是  - 你收回那句话\N{\fs38}- No, you! - You take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fs38}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重攻击\N{\fs38}Double poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们都饿了\N{\fs38}Okay, hope you guys are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了烤通心粉\N{\fs38}Made baked ziti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得用Garibaldi的菜谱会很有意思呢\N{\fs38}Thought it would be fun to use Garibaldi's ultra authentic recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 出于同情的食物\N{\fs38}Oh, great, pity food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样谢谢你 但是我自己可以做饭\N{\fs38}Thank you anyway, but I can cook for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是因为那样脑子会疼的话\N{\fs38}Wow, I would roll my eyes so hard right now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就在翻白眼了\N{\fs38}if it didn't make my brain burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了警监 别闹脾气了\N{\fs38}Okay, Captain, this ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的自尊受到了伤害\N{\fs38}I know your pride is hurt, 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从来没有人同情你\N{\fs38}but no one ever took pity on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想在你不开心的时候帮助你 \N{\fs38}All we wanted to do was help you when you were down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那就是人们在关心彼此的时候会做的事\N{\fs38}Because that's what people do when they care about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会向彼此撒谎\N{\fs38}They tell each other lies 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并无中生有出一些急需解决的案子吗\N{\fs38}and invent urgent mysteries that need to be solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是找点在一起的理由\N{\fs38}Come up with excuses to spend time together
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像问答之夜或者民间艺术节\N{\fs38}like trivia nights or folk art festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有和他们腮腺炎小伙伴Jake一起调查积灰的案子\N{\fs38}Or working old-ass cases with their mumpy boy, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你继续 Amy 我们干得不错\N{\fs38}Back to you, Amy. We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把通心粉吃了 你会喜欢它的\N{\fs38}You're gonna eat this ziti, and you're gonna appreciate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你给我赶紧成熟起来\N{\fs38}and you're gonna grow the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你是对的\N{\fs38}Okay, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为我的行为感到抱歉\N{\fs38}I'm sorry for the way I acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迫不及待要尝尝你的手艺了\N{\fs38}I can't wait to eat your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难吃得要吐了\N{\fs38}Ugh, this is revolting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是什么都没有学到吗\N{\fs38}Wow, have you learned nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比腮腺炎还恐怖 Amy\N{\fs38}That is worse than the mumps, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼\N{\fs38}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全按照Garibaldi的食谱做的\N{\fs38}I used Garibaldi's exact recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我不是个好厨子\N{\fs38}I know I'm not a great cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我超爱听从指示的\N{\fs38}but I love following instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七杯盐\N{\fs38}Seven cups of salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也知道这不会是张菜谱了\N{\fs38}Even I know this isn't a recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这可能是份密码\N{\fs38}Which means it might be a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fs38}Ooh, interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十位数 这可能是个电话号码\N{\fs38}Ten digits, maybe it's a phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 718 布鲁克林区号\N{\fs38}Look, 718, Brooklyn area code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 一定是这样\N{\fs38}Yes, that's definitely it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你真的加了这么多盐\N{\fs38}Wait, did you actually use all of this salt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有18杯牛至\N{\fs38}and 18 cups of oregano?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别管 我破了案子\N{\fs38}Back off, I solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9个洋葱\N{\fs38}Nine onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 Amy\N{\fs38}Oh, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么就成坏人了\N{\fs38}How am I the bad guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.76,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(14.343,586.171,227.899,582.157,39,248)}{\fs45}99分局\N{\fs10}\N{\fs45}3天后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧 这看起来不错\N{\fs38}All right, all right, looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看不出来这里曾经被绿巨人毁灭过一次了\N{\fs38}I can barely tell you hulked out in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是我主管了两周\N{\fs38}Yeah, but two weeks in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一个目标都没有完成\N{\fs38}and I didn't get any of my goals accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让Hitchcock和Scully停止绝食抗议了\N{\fs38}You got Hitchcock and Scully off their hunger strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是把一把爆米花扔到了地上\N{\fs38}I just threw a bunch of popcorn on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不难\N{\fs38}It wasn't that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 他们就像动物一样\N{\fs38}Yeah, they're animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道为什么神奇的Holt警监\N{\fs38}Do you want to know why the amazing Captain Holt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没能清理好证据室\N{\fs38}has never gotten the evidence room cleaned
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者完成你列表上的任何事吗\N{\fs38}or done anything on your list?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs38}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他总在处理同事之间的摩擦\N{\fs38}Because all day long, he's putting out fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是警监的工作\N{\fs38}That's what a captain does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和Holt的唯一区别就是\N{\fs38}The only difference between you and Holt is that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有你这样的神力 关个门就能让一间房散架\N{\fs38}he lacks the strength to close a door so hard a room blows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 Gina\N{\fs38}Thanks, Gina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用感谢我\N{\fs38}Ah, you don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的只是做那个唯一相信你的人\N{\fs38}All I did was be the only person who believes in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠着门\N{\fs38}Don't lean against the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry造成了结构损伤\N{\fs38}Terry caused structural damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 你太壮了\N{\fs38}My God, you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去简报室 现在\N{\fs38}Briefing room, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不想再被你教训了\N{\fs38}I really don't feel like having you yell at me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs38}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Jason的葬礼\N{\fs38}It's a funeral for Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些话想说\N{\fs38}I want to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当七天前Jason去世的时候 我一丁点儿都不在乎\N{\fs38}When Jason died seven days ago, I didn't give a rat's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的发言\N{\fs38}This is your speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不懂为什么人们这么在乎他们蠢兮兮的狗\N{\fs38}'Cause I didn't understand why people care so much about their dumb dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我自己有了一只狗\N{\fs38} till I got a dumb dog myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只养了Arlo一天半\N{\fs38}I've only had Arlo for a day and a half,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果他出了任何事\N{\fs38}but if anything happened to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会杀了这个房间里的所有人然后自杀\N{\fs38}I would kill everyone in this room and then myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常暴力的颂词 我喜欢\N{\fs38}Very violent eulogy, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Charles 我很抱歉\N{\fs38}Charles, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要尽快跨过这道坎\N{\fs38}You don't have to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情沉浸在悲伤吧\N{\fs38}Take as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scully 就现在\N{\fs38}Scully, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢你\N{\fs38}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息 Garibaldi的手机号还在使用\N{\fs38}Good news, Garibaldi's phone number's still active,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们能够找出他的位置\N{\fs38}so they were able to locate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特警刚刚抓住了他 就是这样\N{\fs38}SWAT just picked him up, so that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是这样\N{\fs38}Yeah, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的时间 我们的隔离期终于结束了\N{\fs38}Perfect timing as our quarantine has finally ended
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲状腺肿块也终于消了\N{\fs38}and our goiters are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 没错\N{\fs38}Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以出门去 想舔谁的眼珠就舔谁的眼珠\N{\fs38}We're free to go outside and lick whoever's eyeballs we'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太对 没人有这个权力\N{\fs38}Inaccurate, no one is ever free to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你是对的\N{\fs38}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我出去了\N{\fs38}Anyhow, I am out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等\N{\fs38}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉之前冲你吼叫\N{\fs38}I'm sorry I yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太骄傲了 所以我不想承认我很孤单\N{\fs38}I was too proud to admit I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以谢谢你\N{\fs38}So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气\N{\fs38}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算事儿\N{\fs38}Ain't no thang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这算事儿 更算事儿的是你\N{\fs38}No, it is a thang, and an even bigger thang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回到了99分局\N{\fs38}is that you brought me back to the Nine-Nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远感激这件事的\N{\fs38}and I will always be grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这个\N{\fs38}So, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给你的\N{\fs38}This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酸糖果 我想死你们了\N{\fs38}Sour candies. I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼死我了\N{\fs38}This burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你的礼物\N{\fs38}Thank you for this gift.
